{"tid":1430112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"為香港，我同整個家族鬧交。","createTime":"2019-08-07T16:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:24:26.000Z","uid":65607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"680f1f0e0328cb2c11135d87f86d8ee3ae8451d7","tid":1430112,"uid":65607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:05:00.000Z","msg":"呢嗰係大陸遠房親戚，同佢素未謀面，但之前聽講過佢包二奶，又極度憎恨香港。當年，老母客套同佢講句「得閒去我屋企（香港）坐下」，佢極度大反應咁屌柒香港，話香港人垃圾廢柴，絕對唔會出去。<br />\n但聽講佢嗰女出黎香港生仔，呃資源，但長期定居深圳。出聲之前已經忍咗好多日，佢成日send啲大陸新聞，然後屌柒香港，話最好香港全部示威者比坦克壓死。<br />\n<br />\n終於忍唔住....就斷了六親。 So Sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OmU89my.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOmU89my.png&h=ca75871e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9VMjwzV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9VMjwzV.png&h=7a2abad7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/anATA1B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FanATA1B.png&h=8dcf2cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uX8h2GD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuX8h2GD.png&h=967642a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FfFMbzY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfFMbzY.png&h=073a3611&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vufz4UZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvufz4UZ.png&h=db8c8148&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bE0Xie0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbE0Xie0.png&h=8dad67b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MnzEwz4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.